OL,3,CNottingham Forest sack boss Nuno
OL,4,CEspirito Santo
OL,6,FNottingham Forest has sacked head
OL,7,Fcoach Nuno Espirito Santo following a
OL,8,Fbreakdown in his relationship with
OL,9,Fclub owner Evangelos Marinakis.
OL,11,FThe 51-year-old was only given a new
OL,12,Fcontract in June after guiding Forest
OL,13,Finto the Europa League last term, the
OL,14,Fteam's first European qualification
OL,15,Fsince 1995.
OL,17,FTalks are under way over Nuno's
OL,18,Freplacement, with an appointment
OL,19,Fimminent and former Spurs manager Ange
OL,20,FPostecoglou a contender.
