OL,6,FThe club currently sits 10th in the
OL,7,FPremiere league after losing their
OL,8,Flast match to West Ham 3-0.
OL,10,FIn a statement the club said:
OL,11,F"Nottingham Forest Football Club
OL,12,Fconfirms that, following recent
OL,13,Fcircumstances, Nuno Espirito Santo has
OL,14,Ftoday been relieved of his duties as
OL,15,FHead Coach.
