OL,3,CNottingham Forest sack boss Nuno
OL,4,CEspirito Santo
OL,6,F"The Club thanks Nuno for his
OL,7,Fcontribution during a very successful
OL,8,Fera at the City Ground, in particular
OL,9,Fhis role in the 2024/25 season, which
OL,10,Fwill forever be remembered fondly in
OL,11,Fthe history of the Club.
OL,13,F"As someone who played a pivotal role
OL,14,Fin our success last season, he will
OL,15,Falways hold a special place in our
OL,16,Fjourney."
OL,18,FForest officials were said to have
OL,19,Fbeen taken by surprise when Nuno
OL,20,Fpublicly revealed his broken
OL,21,Frelationship with Marinakis last month.
