OL,4,CEspirito Santo
OL,6,FResponding to rumours about his
OL,7,Fposition at the time, Nuno admitted
OL,8,F"where there's smoke, there's fire",
OL,9,Ffirst raising questions about his
OL,10,Ffuture at the club.
OL,12,F"We know each other very well, and we
OL,13,Fhave all been in the industry for a
OL,14,Fwhile now," he said of Marinakis ahead
OL,15,Fof their Premier League game against
OL,16,FCrystal Palace.
OL,18,F"And where there's smoke, there's
OL,19,Ffire, so I know how things work, but
OL,20,FI'm here to do my job.
