OL,6,F"I understand, because I'm worried.
OL,7,FI'm the first one to be worried. I'm
OL,8,Fthe first one to be concerned."
OL,10,FPreviously, Nuno had criticised the
OL,11,Fclub's activity in the summer transfer
OL,12,Fwindow, saying they had wasted a good
OL,13,Fchance, despite spending almost
OL,14,F#100million on the likes of James
OL,15,FMcAtee, Omari Hutchinson, Arnaud
OL,16,FKalimuendo and Douglas Luiz.
