OL,6,FAnd Nuno added: "I always had a very
OL,7,Fgood relationship with the owner, last
OL,8,Fseason was very, very, very close.
OL,9,FThis season, not so well. No, it's not
OL,10,F(good)."
OL,12,FHaving led the club into Europe, Nuno
OL,13,Fdeparts the City Ground as the club's
OL,14,Fmost successful manager since Frank
OL,15,FClark, and they currently sit 10th in
OL,16,Fthe Premier League table.
